are.  Yes we could argue all day about how good a wiz is at dueling..is it possibl;e to take out any class ...i would say yes....is it likely to take out some classes? I would say no.  PvP figths ar enot the nice organized XP group s where we fight till oom and med up. There is no way we are gonna take out multiple melee types of the apropiate levels.  We juust don't have the mana.  Someone hit it on the head earlier about why they won't increase the damage....solability.  Casters in general are already excelenet soloers compared to meleees.  There already is a trean i would venture to say that necros generally don't group ..they would prefer to solo.  its even been said on this board if you want xp you go solo and quad kite. So what would happen if you increase dam besides the fact we would be more helpful in xp groups?  We would be unstoppable in Soloing.  That is why we don't get increased damage.<br>
